<section xml:id="sec-section-two" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  
  <title>Quadratic Equation</title>
  <activity>
    <statement>
        <p>
            solve the quadratic equation given below:
        </p>
        <p>
            a. <m>x^2+3x+2=0</m>
        </p>

    </statement>
    <hint>
    <p>There are many ways of solving quadratic equations.it can either be : </p>
    <p>a. use of factorization method eg <m>(a-b)(a+b)=0</m>.</p>
    <p>b. use of quadratic formula that is <m>x=\frac{-b\pm\sqrt{b^2-4ac}}{2a}</m>.</p>
    <p>c. Use of compliting square method that is ensurering that the the equation given is written ina perfect square form eg <m>(a+b)(a+b)=0</m> and <m>ac=(\frac{b}{2})^2</m></p>
    <p>d. the graphical method is also way of finding the roots of the equation</p>
    <p><em>In this case lets consider the quadratic formula in order to solve this exersise given below</em></p>
    <p>supose we have this question:    <m>x^2-1=0</m></p>
    <p>By the quadratic fomula above it implies that <m>a=1</m> <m>b=0</m> and <m>c=1</m></p>
    <p>subtituiting in the formula <m>x=\frac{0\pm\sqrt{-4\times1\times-1}}{2\times1}</m> </p>
    <p>                              <m>x=\frac{\pm\sqrt{4}}{2}</m></p>
    <p>                              <m>x=\frac{\pm{2}}{2}</m> </p>
    <p>                              <m>x=1</m>   or  <m>x=-1</m>   </p>

  </hint>
  <solution>
    <p> Given <m>x^2+3x+2=0</m> where <m>a=1  b=3 and c=2</m> substitute in the formula 
    <m>x=\frac{-b\pm\sqrt{b^2-4ac}}{2a}</m></p> 
      <p>
        <md>
          <mrow> x=\amp\frac{-3\pm\sqrt{(-3)^2-4\times 1 \times2}}{2\times1} </mrow>
          <mrow> =\amp \frac{-3\pm\sqrt{9-(4\times 1 \times 2)}}{2} </mrow>
          <mrow> =\amp\frac{-3\pm\sqrt{9-(8)}}{2} </mrow>
          <mrow> =\amp \frac{-3\pm\sqrt{1}}{2} </mrow>
          <mrow> =\amp \frac{-3\pm 1}{2}</mrow>
          <mrow> =\amp\frac{-3+ 1}{2}  \text{or} </mrow>
          <mrow> =\amp \frac{-3-1}{2}</mrow>
          <mrow> x_1=\amp-1   </mrow>
          <mrow>x_2 =\amp -2 </mrow>
        </md>
        <men xml:id="eqn4-solution"> x=-1 \;\text{ or }\;  x=-2
          
        </men>
        The soluition is as shown <xref ref="eqn4-solution"/>
        
      </p>
  </solution>
  </activity>

    


   



  
